model.interpreter.custom

Class TimelineVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.interpreter.core.FetchVisitor
      • model.interpreter.custom.TimelineVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResumeVisitor

    public class TimelineVisitor
extends FetchVisitor
    This interpreter transforms the consumed model into a JSONP-Format. For each resume in the model one json file will be created. These files can be used as input for the great "TimmelineJS"-Tool (see http://timeline.verite.co/).
    Author:
    Christoph Petzold
